==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''to [[champ]] at the [[bit]]'''
#(''of a horse'') to [[bite]] the [[bit]], especially when [[restless]]
#(''of a person'') to show [[impatience]] or [[frustration]] when [[delayed]]
[[Category:English idioms]]
#:''The supercomputer is complete, and scientists are '''champing at the bit''' to use it.''

